      • getPdfReaderWithLock

        static com.lowagie.text.pdf.PdfReader getPdfReaderWithLock(File file,
                                                           byte[] lock)
                                                    throws IOException
        Case #38484 CRN170613 We can have a problem when dealing with older files that use our older password locking system. If we try to open an older file that uses the older locking system, we won't be able to open it with our new system. This method hides the extra lines of code needed to try the old system password to open a file if we fail to open the file with the new new system password.
        Parameters:
        file - file that will be read in to the PdfReader
        lock - the proposed lock bytes that should be used to create the PdfReader
        Returns:
        the PdfReader that corresponds to the passed-in file
        Throws:
        IOException
